2014-01-02  Glenn Randers-Pehrson  <glennrp@simple.dallas.tx.us>

	* coders/png.c (ReadOnePNGImage): Don't use libpng function
	png_set_scale_16_to_8() when scaling 16-bit input PNG down to
	8-bit in a Q8 build.  "scale" is more accurate, but the slight
	difference causes reference tests to fail and causes unexpected
	difference between the behavior of PNG and other formats.  So
	we simply let the GM import routines do the job.

